To install React Router, follow these steps:
Step 1: Navigate to Your Project Directory
Open your terminal and navigate to the directory of your React project:
cd your-project-directory
npm install react-router-dom

After installation, check if react-router-dom is listed in your package.json dependencies:
json
Copy code
"dependencies": {
  "react-router-dom": "^6.x.x"
}

import and use react router
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"; in app.js

